graph TD
  %% Initialization
  Z[Frontend UI] -->|Injects soil_type & Lat/Lon into Message| A
  A[Agent requests Tool Call] --> B{Which Tool?}
  
  %% The Interceptor Flow
  B -- fetch_graph --> C[Execute ClickHouse SQL]
  C --> D[Save array to Request.state.buffer]
  D --> E[Return basic 'Success' string to Agent]
  
  %% The Standard/Decider Flow
  B -- custom_agronomy_tools --> F[Execute DB Logic]
  F --> G{Try/Except DB Error?}
  
  %% The Self-Healing Loop
  G -- Yes (Exception Caught) --> H[Extract error message]
  H --> I[Return raw Error String to Agent]
  I --> |Agent retries up to 3x| A
  
  %% Success Flow
  G -- No (Success) --> J[Return JSON string to Agent]
  
  %% Final Assembly
  E --> K[Agent generates final Text]
  J --> K
  K --> L[FastAPI bundles Text + chart_data buffer into ChatResponse]